extendedInfo.description: Everybody wins at Dealfind!Dealfind features amazing deals offering you up to 90% off every day! When you see a deal you want to purchase, just click the 'Buy' button before the deal expires, so make sure you act quickly and you'll be ready to save! Get ready to eat, play, shop and relax as you discover the best your city has to offer!Dealfind apps lets you:- Login to your account or sign-up for an account- View all the deals available in each city- View details about a specific deal- Buy a deal on the go- Redeem Promo Codes- View all your vouchers
